e of globalization. He writes with unmatched intensity and a unique sensitivity to the human tragicomedy.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 0aRomanian fiction. 0aRomanian literature. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh1 aMarian, Oana Sanziana, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z97831105379940 cprintz978030017994140uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030018346740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300183467423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300183467/original  a978-3-11-053799-4  Yale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-UCY